linthesia (0.7.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Use version from buildsystem
  * Remove excludes from ignores
  * fix: add desktop and icon to correct paths
  * fix: compilation due to missing graphics file
  * feat: improved keyboard on wide screens (#7)
  * chore: use c++17
  * feat: choosing keyboard size in title screen (#6)
  * feat(text): improved text sharpness and shadows (#5)
  * fix: fixed keybindings (#4)
  * fix: delay screensaver using SDL
  * refactor(graphics): ported to SDL
  * fix(drawing): support for smooth high fps
  * fix(user-settings): replaced gconfmm with gconf
  * Do not lauch FullScreen : - Requires to do -W for fullscreen or -w for windowed. - FIX required for detecting jail (default fullscreen was nice).
  * Do not try to read seq if seq has failed
  * Load EVERY font found on system. When one works, use it.
  * CrashFix : avoid SIGSEGV or throwing kill signals Just play without characters
  * BUGFIX : print a more verbose error when crashing with pangofont problem
  * Fix path selection for files
  * Creating PNG icon. Deleting xpm files (except in "extra" that is not used).
  * Recalculate "Track Selection" screen on resize.
  * Add sqlite3
  * Add musicdir atoutoconf param
  * Add 'title_Dirbox.tga' in installed tools
  * Add key names rendering
  * Fix folder back button behaviour when hit not from the first page
  * Fix textures and paths
  * Fix paths
  * Add cmd options for min and max keys on keyboard
  * remove options button from device tile
  * Add simple command line argument parsing for windowed mode and file
  * Ignore notes out of range
  * Manage music path
  * More icons
