  * Add path navigation for SongLibState
  * Songs lib - first working iteration
  * Resize and windw mode
  * fix with-scriptdir help string
  * quote SCRIPTDIR and GRAPHDIR to make it compatible with existing code
  * return bindir as default for scriptdir
  * make resource directories configurable
  * choose monitor contains pointer
  * Add continuous integration
  * Match bars and retry positions
  * Hit all notes that start before retry
  * Use Page Up/Page Down to scroll song position
  * Keep is_retry_on when switching between Playing and TrackSelection states
  * Do not count retry until first key press
  * Fix non-zero note offset in retry-mode
  * Add retry on and off buttons
  * Add more sprites: computer, human, retry
  * Add splited InterfaceButtons
  * Handle device connecting/disconnecting on the title page
